..TEXT:
|ch'~ = ^ch$e~ (^perch$e~); the antecedent is "da indi
in l@a" taken as meaning "that which lies beyond," i.e., beyond
the confines of natural reason.  The meaning of Virgil and
Beatrice in the allegory is rather clearly disclosed through
these verses.  |opra~ = ^opera.~
