..TEXT:
|di ritenerlo @e in voi la podestate~: Each and every
love may be awakened in us of necessity, but it lies within our
power to check it, at the first stage of love, and before the
inclination and complacency in the object which is properly so
termed becomes a desire and moves toward possession of the
object, thus crossing the "threshold of assent."
