..TEXT:
|la gente a cui il mar s'aperse~: The Israelites,
who were sluggish and recalcitrant in crossing the desert after
the Lord had caused the waters of the Red Sea to divide so that
they marched across it as on dry land, while the Egyptians
perished in it.
