..TEXT:
|che vedesse Iordan le rede sue~: See Num. 14:1-39,
especially vs. 23: "Non videbunt terram pro qua iuravi patribus
eorum; nec quisquam ex illis qui detraxit mihi intuebitur eam."
("Not one shall see the land which I promised on oath to their
fathers.  None of these who have spurned me shall see it.")
Joshua and Caleb were the two exceptions; aside from them, only
those Israelites who had been born in the desert reached the
Promised Land.
..TCHR:
